Riwiki
======

Riwiki is Rails plugin which adds wiki functionality to your Rails application.

Installation
============

In your application directory call:
  script/plugin install git://github.com/alno/riwiki

Usage
=====

Add to your @routes.rb@ something like:
  map.riwiki_root '/wiki'

